description.narrative: The Government of Sudan is better equipped to prioritize, implement and address emerging issues in the WASH sector, drawing upon new evidence and UNICEF's technical support for strategies and plans and improved capacity for monitoring and reporting through the developed Sudan WASH SDG6 plan, states ODF road maps and web-based WASH IMS.
